{
  "texts": [
    "At present, the UCI database has reached more than 1,000 citations, making it one of the top 100 most cited in computer science.",
    "According to the dataset range studied in this paper, that is, open data sets aiming at classification that can be converted into structured data through simple or slightly complex operations, open datasets included in UCI database are selected.",
    "One hundred and thirty-eight independent datasets from 335 UCI datasets were included in the study.",
    "The datasets in the UCI database come from various industries, and a considerable part of them are shared raw data.",
    "10.3389/fncom.2024.1345575 Frontiers in Computational Neuroscience 04 frontiersin.org"
  ]
}